s. beth did careful research.\\nso why did beth even bite?\\n\\n> because she knows how this game works\\n> it's not about whether SHE'S careful\\n> it's about who gets to define what \\\"autism self-diagnosis\\\" means in everyone's head\\n\\nscott calls this the \\\"weak man\\\" and honestly it explains everything wrong with the internet\\n\\n> a straw man is when you make up a guy to beat up\\n> a weak man is when you find the dumbest real person in a group and make everyone fight them\\n\\nlike atheists and the westboro baptist church\\nyeah those guys are real. yeah they suck.\\nbut if every argument about religion becomes about westboro...\\nand westboro keeps losing...\\nthen in people's minds religion = westboro = losing argument = dumb\\n\\n> and suddenly your normal episcopalian neighbor who just likes christmas\\n> is spending 5 minutes apologizing for fred phelps before he can say anything\\n> congrats you killed religion without ever debating a real theologian\\n\\nthis is the superweapon\\nand once you see it you can't unsee it\\n\\n> imagine being a jew in russia circa 1900\\n> day 1: \\\"a jew killed a christian kid\\\" - well it happened, can't argue\\n> day 2: \\\"the jews killed christ\\\" - it's their religion man, not my place\\n> day 3: \\\"jewish bankers ruining the economy\\\" - well statistically...\\n> day 4: \\\"israeli atrocities\\\" - yeah some of that is real\\n> day 5: neighbor won't pay you back \\\"because everyone knows jews are christ-killing money-grubbing murderers\\\"\\n> you never defended ANY of those statements individually\\n> but now you're fucked anyway\\n\\nthat's the trap\\neach statement was technically about SOMEONE ELSE\\nnone of them were about YOU\\nbut they stacked up into a weapon that hits everyone in the group\\n\\n> this is why \\\"not all men\\\" drives feminists insane\\n> and also why men keep saying it\\n\\nfeminists say \\\"some men harass women\\\"\\nguy hears it as \\\"men harass women\\\"\\nguy says \\\